{# Jinja2 template — qa-response-templates
   Used by: shareholder-inquiry-router and analyst-question-classifier agents
   Variables: audience (retail|institutional), question_category, analyst_name,
              analyst_firm, question_text, approved_answer (may be empty),
              ir_contact_name, company_name, ir_website_url
   Reg FD note: DRAFT — all responses are internal until HotL-approved.
#}
<!-- DRAFT — INTERNAL USE ONLY — NOT APPROVED FOR EXTERNAL DISTRIBUTION -->

{% if audience == 'retail' %}
---
**To:** {{ sender_name | default("Investor") }}
**From:** {{ ir_contact_name | default("[IR Contact]") }}, Investor Relations
**Re:** Your inquiry regarding {{ company_name }}
**Date:** {{ today }}

Dear {{ sender_name | default("Investor") }},

Thank you for your interest in {{ company_name }}. We appreciate you reaching out
to our Investor Relations team.

{% if approved_answer %}
{{ approved_answer }}
{% else %}
[APPROVED ANSWER REQUIRED — do not send without content from IR team]
{% endif %}

For additional information, we invite you to visit our investor relations website
at {{ ir_website_url | default("[IR website URL]") }}, where you will find our
most recent earnings releases, SEC filings, investor presentations, and FAQs.

If you have further questions, please don't hesitate to contact us at
{{ ir_email | default("[ir@company.com]") }}.

Best regards,
{{ ir_contact_name | default("[IR Contact Name]") }}
Investor Relations
{{ company_name }}

---
{% endif %}

{% if audience == 'institutional' %}
---
**To:** {{ analyst_name | default("[Analyst Name]") }}, {{ analyst_firm | default("[Firm]") }}
**From:** {{ ir_contact_name | default("[IR Contact]") }}, Investor Relations — {{ company_name }}
**Re:** Response to your inquiry — {{ question_category | upper }} matter
**Date:** {{ today }}
**Classification:** Institutional Investor Response — IR-Lead Review Required

Dear {{ analyst_name | default("[Analyst Name]") }},

Thank you for your question regarding {{ company_name }}. We appreciate your
continued engagement as an institutional shareholder.

{% if question_category == 'financial' %}
**Category: Financial**
Our response is based solely on publicly disclosed financial information in our
most recent SEC filings and earnings releases. We are unable to comment on
information beyond what has been publicly disclosed.

{% elif question_category == 'strategic' %}
**Category: Strategic**
We appreciate your interest in our strategic direction. Our response is limited
to information already disclosed in public communications.

{% elif question_category == 'operational' %}
**Category: Operational**
We are pleased to address your operational question within the bounds of
publicly available information.

{% elif question_category == 'competitive' %}
**Category: Competitive**
We do not comment on competitor-specific information. Our response focuses
on our own publicly disclosed operational and financial data.

{% elif question_category == 'esg' %}
**Category: ESG**
Thank you for your focus on our ESG performance. Our response draws from our
most recent ESG/sustainability report and public disclosures.
{% endif %}

{% if approved_answer %}
{{ approved_answer }}
{% else %}
[APPROVED ANSWER REQUIRED — this section must be completed by the
responsible team ({{ routed_to | default("IR-Lead") }}) and approved before send]
{% endif %}

Please note that this communication does not constitute selective disclosure.
Any material information referenced herein is available to the general public
through our SEC filings and investor relations website.

We welcome further dialogue. Please feel free to schedule a call with our IR team.

Best regards,
{{ ir_contact_name | default("[IR Contact Name]") }}
Investor Relations — {{ company_name }}
{{ ir_website_url | default("[IR website URL]") }}

<!-- IR-Lead: please confirm this response does not contain MNPI before approving -->
---
{% endif %}

{% if audience == 'activist' %}
